cells.data: -- lookupDict :: a -> Dict -> Maybe bon lookupDict(k, dct)	set ca to current application	set v to (ca's NSDictionary's dictionaryWithDictionary:dct)'s objectForKey:k	if v â‰  missing value then		Just(item 1 of ((ca's NSArray's arrayWithObject:v) as list))	else		Nothing()	end ifend lookupDict
